    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      141.73,
      542.76,
      182.61
    ],
    "text": "On the afternoon of 1 July 2026, officers of the Colombo Central Divisional Criminal Investigation Bureau, acting on intelligence information, conducted a raid in the Ferguson Road area of Mattakkuliya, within the Mattakkuliya Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      197.17,
      528.79,
      265.68
    ],
    "text": "During the operation, officers arrested a suspect in possession of 5 kilograms and 140 grams of heroin, Rs. 50,000 suspected to be proceeds from illicit drug trafficking, and two mobile phones believed to have been used in the trafficking operation. The suspect and the recovered items were subsequently handed over to the Mattakkuliya Police Station.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      280.12,
      365.47,
      293.4
    ],
    "text": "The suspect is a 40-year-old resident of Colombo 10.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      307.96,
      450.7,
      321.24
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by the Mattakkuliya Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
