      72.79
    ],
    "text": "On the evening of 1 July 2026, officers of the Walana Central Anti-Corruption Unit, acting on intelligence information, conducted a raid in the Podiweekumbura area within the Ragama Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
